{"tid":1610702,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日上過前同得個濕鳩口罩個啲同我入黎","createTime":"2019-10-01T19:14:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T19:20:20.000Z","uid":200731,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ed070a9ba73d00b2a81949ff2754bd3aba4f7bcb","tid":1610702,"uid":200731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:14:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OkC6SEe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOkC6SEe.png&h=0f3babbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n講撚左幾多次Black Bloc包頭呀<br />\n一件黑tee就做到 咁簡單希望大家做<br />\n3年前魚革手足包到咩樣講革命<br />\n然後你3年後得口罩😷<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一枝長鏡就影哂你地樣啦<br />\n<br />\n次次行街前都有手足係到呼籲要包頭要black bloc<br />\n要攝衫唔著背心短褲<br />\n<br />\n然後呢屌你地得個濕鳩口罩😷<br />\n最後好多謝今日每一個手足 家長<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"36d54ced5e116747a5e737b98fe4868c54eb727f","tid":1610702,"uid":200731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed070a9ba73d00b2a81949ff2754bd3aba4f7bcb","tid":1610702,"uid":200731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:14:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OkC6SEe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOkC6SEe.png&h=0f3babbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n講撚左幾多次Black Bloc包頭呀<br />\n一件黑tee就做到 咁簡單希望大家做<br />\n3年前魚革手足包到咩樣講革命<br />\n然後你3年後得口罩😷<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一枝長鏡就影哂你地樣啦<br />\n<br />\n次次行街前都有手足係到呼籲要包頭要black bloc<br />\n要攝衫唔著背心短褲<br />\n<br />\n然後呢屌你地得個濕鳩口罩😷<br />\n最後好多謝今日每一個手足 家長<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:19:54.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid"